                  <additions>
                    <list>
                      <item xml:id = "a1">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target = "#118v"/> <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer whose purpose is not stated, with incipit: <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ታኬም፡ ኬሮአኬም፡ ኬሮፔ፡ ሃፋሴ፡ ኃይለ፡ ቀራቶም፡...፯ጊዜ፡ ድግ[ም]።</foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a2">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target = "#118v"/> <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer and medical prescription for help in learning, with incipit <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አላⷓ፡ ኢላኽያ፡ ኤላኽ፡ የበለስ፡ ተቀጽላ፡ ሕፃን፡ አርብ፡ ረቡዕ፡ ይቁረጥ፡</foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a3">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target = "#118v #119r"/> <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer whose purpose is not stated, with incipit: <foreign xml:id = "gez">እንፈረው፡ አስልጥቤ፡ እንፈሸው፡ እነሩኅሉቤ፡ ወኢላሃኩም፡ ኢላሁ፡ ዋሂዱ፡ ኢለለ፡ ሀይለላ፡ ወረሂማን፡ ወረሂብ፡...</foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a4">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target = "#119r #120v"/>: <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer against fever and pestilence,
                          with incipit: <foreign xml:lang = "gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡...ጸልት፡ በእንተ፡ ፌራ፡ ወቸነፈር፡ ሕማመ፡ በሽታ፡ ወተስሕቦ፡ ዘያድኅን፡ ወትብል፡ በትሑት፡ ቃል፡ እሎንተ፡ አስማተ፡ ዓቢያተ፡ ኤኮስ፡ ለሚእለኬ፡...
                          በጸሎቱ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ በጸሎታ፡ ወበስእለታ፡...</foreign>.
                          Incomplete in the middle, erased to make room for the pictures.
                          It is not even clear if it is one prayer, but cf. Abbadie 206, f. 19v, Conti Rossini, Notice, no. 136
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a5">
                        <desc type = "OwnershipNote">Note of ownership by <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ቸኮል፡ ገብረ፡ ስላሴ፡</foreign> and his wife <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ወለተ፡ ሚካኤል፡</foreign>, <locus target = "#120v"/></desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a6">
                        <desc>Copied by <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ወልደ፡ ገብርኤል፡</foreign>, <locus target = "#118r"/></desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a7">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target = "#32v"/>, upper margin: John 5:45–47 is written and a mark at the end of column 2, line 7 indicates where the text belongs
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a8">
                        <desc>
                          Overlooked words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target = "#26r #33v #39r"/>);
                          and overlooked lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target = "#27r #40v #110r"/>);
                          and in the upper margin with a symbol (+) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target = "#15r"/>, line 4 and <locus target = "#40r"/>, line 4),
                          and in another case where the symbol (I) is used (<locus target = "#32v"/>, line 7)
                        </desc>
                      </item>
